# Custom environment variables for Edge Functions (optional).
#
# Only create `supabase/functions/.env` if your function needs extra secrets/config.
# Keep the real `supabase/functions/.env` uncommitted.
#
# Local:
#   supabase functions serve --env-file supabase/functions/.env
#
# Hosted:
#   supabase secrets set --env-file supabase/functions/.env
#
# Important:
# - `supabase functions serve` ignores env var names starting with `SUPABASE_`.
# - The runtime provides `SUPABASE_URL`, `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`, etc automatically.
#
# Example:
# MY_CUSTOM_SECRET=

